messages.msgSnippet: Hi, Debra! Here are some paperdoll websites I have - they re great to print out on cardstock! Paper
messages.messageBody:
Hi, Debra!

Here are some paperdoll websites I have - they're great to print out on
cardstock!

<A HREF="http://www.wwvisions.com/craftbb/paperdoll.html">Paper Doll
Bulletin Board</A>
<A HREF="http://www.dreamhaven.net/~liana/paperdolls/index.html">Liana's
Paper Doll Boutique - Paper Dolls and Paper Doll Clothes</A>
<A HREF="http://www.ameritech.net/users/macler/paperdolls.html">Marilee's
Paperdolls Page: Printable Paperdolls, Links, Books</A>
<A HREF="http://www.nikolai.com/RUMPUSRM/playpage/papernw/default.htm">Paper
Neow</A> - lots of paper stuff
<A HREF="http://www.geocities.com/Athens/Olympus/6626/paper.html">Paper Dolls
</A> - Hercules paperdolls

Have fun!

Linda in FL :) (who LOVES paper dolls!)
